---
title: Sticky Pistachio Crusted Salmon with Herby Feta Bulgur Wheat, Roasted Red Pepper and Rocket
description: We love good Sticky Pistachio Crusted Salmon and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
